OL,3,CIllegal drugs in staff locker at
OL,4,CUniversity Hospital in Wales, review
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe review heard reports of illegal
OL,8,Fdrugs being found in a staff locker. A
OL,9,Fpolice investigation into the incident
OL,10,Fdid not lead to charges, due to lack
OL,11,Fof evidence.
OL,13,FFollowing a disciplinary process, the
OL,14,Fmember of staff continues to work at
OL,15,Fthe health board.
OL,17,FCardiff and Vale University health
OL,18,Fboard has apologised to staff and said
OL,19,Fthey on they are working on plan for
OL,20,Fthe best way to proceed.
