OL,3,CIllegal drugs in staff locker at
OL,4,CUniversity Hospital in Wales, review
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe 22 page report, by Cardiff and
OL,8,FVales University's health board
OL,9,Fdescribes "systematic failure" within
OL,10,Fthe Mains Theatres Upper Leadership
OL,11,Fteam, where an "atmosphere of fear"
OL,12,Fprevented staff from raising concerns.
OL,14,FIt also highlighted an incident in
OL,15,Fwhich a senior member of staff
OL,16,Fallegedly commented that a group of
OL,17,FIndian nurses needed name badges
OL,18,Fbecause they "all looked the same".
