OL,4,CUniversity Hospital in Wales, review
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FIt concluded racist remarks had been
OL,8,Fmade, and following a disciplinary
OL,9,Fprocess, the individual in question
OL,10,Fhas returned to work due to
OL,11,Finsufficient evidence.
OL,13,FThe reviewing team, who work at the
OL,14,Fhospital but are independent of the
OL,15,Ftheatre teams, heard from 113 staff
OL,16,Fduring a six month period.
OL,18,FThe theatres department in UHW sees
OL,19,Faround 30,000 patients per year, with
OL,20,Faround 250 members of staff.
